/addons/

# ---- Viewer runtime artifact ----
# curve.json is the cached Δv-vs-lead sweep the egui app loads: a regenerable
# product of `cargo run -p viewer --bin curve` (a fixed property of the designed
# scenario), not a source or a committed validation fixture. Root-only so it does
# not shadow the committed pyref/ *.json fixtures.
/curve.json

